{"tid":738313,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（領養貓貓）有冇人養過近親繁殖嘅貓？多唔多病痛？","createTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T07:58:11.000Z","uid":172953,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8afb65f169e1bbc7b3e1fd3597f3a602165340e7","tid":738313,"uid":172953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:18:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過養近親繁殖出黎嘅貓貓？<br />\n或者聽過身邊有人養過呢類既貓？<br />\n因為遲啲我打算領養一隻貓b返黎養<br />\n但係隻貓B係由同一胎嘅兄妹生嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想知亂倫出黎嘅貓貓會唔會好大問題<br />\n暫時睇唔出有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又驚養養下有咩嚴重嘅病醫唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以問下各位巴絲嘅意見<br />\n附上貓貓j圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/201747_071d3437cf036e3f7e3bc17f0352f7e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F201747_071d3437cf036e3f7e3bc17f0352f7e0.png&h=8ce68586&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/201748_42d95e94430b3279283e97016a4f9561.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F201748_42d95e94430b3279283e97016a4f9561.png&h=7eb31bb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"548c3921f3515a58b7b1b780ca23fe3cc7b7e8e4","tid":738313,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n我果隻係近親繁殖出黎的<br />\n不育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29200a6c1c759128db24465e4a4574a790eec71","tid":738313,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548c3921f3515a58b7b1b780ca23fe3cc7b7e8e4","tid":738313,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":